snippet.title: Johnny Depp Has to Pay Amber Heard This Amount in Divorce Settlement | WHOSAY
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard reached a divorce settlement. The 'Pirates of the Caribbean' actor is reportedly paying his ex-wife $7 million.
